To run the baseline model,
go to the directory and type in:
  python Baseline.py

To run the baseline improved model,
stay in the same directory and type in the terminal:
  python Improved_Baseline.py

To run the trigram HMM model,
stay in the same directory and type in the terminal:
  python Trigramhmm.py

To run the trigram HMM improved,
stary in the same directory and type in the terminal:
  python Improved_Trigramhmm.py
